init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the 92nd little pig was like, "The wolf is not going to blow up my house."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf was like, "I'm the Big Bad Wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig was like, "bring it on, sucka."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He blew his wolf whistle and a bunch of wolves came.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf and the group of wolves were like, "we're going to blow up that pig's house."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf and the group of wolves tried to blow up the pig's house for three days and three nights but they just couldn't do it

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The other wolves ate him, and then they all got dysentery from the wolf meat.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig was like, "ha ha, suckers!"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Big Bad Wolf and the Big Bad Elephant were standing in front of his house with a bunch of other elephants.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "What up, piggy?" said the Big Bad Wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We're here to save you from the radiation poisoning."

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: "We're here to save you from the radiation poisoning."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You thought we were done with you, huh?

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig stared at the Big Bad Elephant gang.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You brought your crew, huh?" said the 92nd little pig.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You're going to need a bigger crew."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "We are the biggest," said Big Bad Wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He loaded it and aimed it at the Big Bad Wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: he said as he blew up the Big Bad Wolf's gang and all of Bambi's relatives.
